edu.ata.user

Class Logger.Urgency

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ata.user.Logger.Urgency
  • Enclosing class:
    Logger

    public static final class Logger.Urgency
extends Object
    Class representing the urgency of the log. The reason for this implementation is to ensure that logging does not encounter an error when looking at its urgency. (Ex. int could be out of range, etc.) This keeps the only possible values to be pre-approved by this class. (No errors when logging)
